 freshmeat linuxntfs
      desc 'library and tools for NTFS modification
ntfsprogs provides Linux drivers and
user space tools for the proprietary filesystem
used by Windows NT, 2000, XP, and 2003.
It also provides support for the Logical Disk Manager
(LDM) that controls Windows Dynamic Disks and is used
to create software Mirrors, Stripes, RAID, etc.'
